# Report

### Coal storage at position (5.5, -57.5)
Consists of a wooden chest at position (5.5, -57.5)

## ERROR TIPS

### Errors when inserting items into a furnace
- The agent's inventory is full, preventing it from picking up and inserting coal into the furnace at (-15.0, -50.0). Ensure the inventory has enough free slots before attempting to insert items.

### Errors due to lack of wooden chests
- The agent attempts to use wooden chests but does not have enough in its inventory. Ensure that the agent crafts or obtains enough wooden chests before attempting to place them.
